          <h5>Annual Membership Fees </h5>
            <li>Junior Membership : £7.00</li>
            <li>Senior Membership : £15.00</li>
            <li>Family Membership : £30.00</li>
            <p>(Membership requires renewal at the start of each season in September)</p>
            <p>Joining is simple: just go down to the ski hut during session hours and speak to any one of the committee members or helpers. Or click here to see how to contact us.</p>
            <p><a class="btn btn-info" href="contact">Contact us &raquo;</a></p>
