        <h4>Experienced speed demons</h4>
        <p>All members of the ski club are eligible to race.
        It's a great way to improve your skiing so if you are interested in racing then contact Tony, or any member of the team, who will provide you with the information you need. Alternativly have a look at our racing team page</P>
         <p><a class="btn btn-info" href="team">Racing team &raquo;</a></p>
