        <h4>Fun friendly family</h4>
        <p>Occasionally we run family sessions so adults and kids can ski together. All skiers must be able to turn and stop safely to ski during these sessions. The dates can be viewed on the events page, along with other social activites that are arranged by our social secretary Jane.
        Note that during these sessions there will be no instruction.</P>
